    "description": "<strong>Test your scrambled word skills in head-to-head competition</strong><br><br>Use your word skills to outscore your opponent(s) using word stacking and socking techniques.<br>Optionally, games can be timed with per-move or per-game timers.<br>Play locally in solo mode or with up to four players. Includes AI players of all levels from first-grader to expert wordsmith.<br>Play online in multiplayer lobbies with up to four players.<br><br>Game requires keyboard and mouse, although a gamepad is possible by using Steam's controller mapping.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Map controller buttons of your choice to the Escape and Shift keys<br></li><li>Map a controller button to the left mouse button<br></li><li>(Optional) Map a controller button to the right mouse button (this allows removing an entire play from the board with one button)<br></li><li>Map a joystick or pad to the left mouse cursor position.</li></ul>With this setup, functionality will be sufficient to play, but for timed games, fast word typing will not be possible.<br><br>Multiplayer requires:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>a valid Steam client and profile <br></li><li>a working internet connection.</li></ul>",
